data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.5% loan available on this home! Enjoy luxury living at its finest in this EXQUISITE estate home in the exclusive gated community Governors Towne Country and Golf Club. Situated on a beautiful .71 acre lot with unobstructed views of the golf course from all of the amazing outdoor living spaces. This luxurious home features 5 bedrooms, 5.5 baths, an oversized 1200 sq ft. 3 car garage, car charger, custom full finished basement with a full bar and additional kitchen, game area, putting green, extra living space and resort style  pool/ hot tub! Stunning open concept floor plan that boasts a perfect blend of warm and modern design with so much attention to detail, 8" hickory hard flooring and upgraded finishes throughout! Spacious chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances, oversized island and walk in pantry. Two spacious living areas on the main level both featuring a custom fireplace and bookshelves, lots of windows and natural light, a wine/ spirits bar that includes a beverage cooler, ice maker and microwave. Walk right out from the main living areas to the covered deck with a fireplace and fire pit table that overlooks the custom pool and sweeping views of golf course. The gorgeous oversized master suite is on the main level featuring a large SPA like bathroom, enormous upgraded stone shower, soaking tub, his/hers vanities, a dream custom walk in closet with an island and its own deck with views. All of the spacious secondary bedrooms have their own private full upgraded bathrooms and walk in closets. The terrace level is perfect for entertaining complete with a custom expansive bar, serving buffet and 2nd kitchen, game area, PGA putting green area, wine cellar room, another living space, private large guest suite with a full bathroom that could be an in-law or teenager suite and extra rooms for storage. Control 4 smart home security system and automation throughout. Relax and unwind in your own amazing fenced backyard oasis featuring a heated color changing gunite pebble tech pool, hot tub with water/fire features, imported travertine decking, multiple patio spaces and decks overlooking the 6th hole of the golf course! Governor's Towne Club offers so many amenities including a full service clubhouse with golf club, 18 hole championship golf course, restaurants, spa, fitness club, tennis facility, olympic size pool with waterslide, baseball field and playground. You do not want to miss this one of a kind EXTRAORDINARY dream home!
